Here's Dog Knight RPG created by (Chris Humphries).
A semi work in progress comic series that started around late 2020 (July 7, 2020).

"*Summary*

This is a fantasy comic series about a traveling dog knight named Rory. She explores the war ridden, monster infested lands of Ulfraya with her party of optimistic and weird adventurers. Together, the party tackles the many perils of fantasy adventuring one measly gold coin at a time." - Artist.
